    "description": "对齐飞书 Wiki《【预测市场】体育频道列表页全品类接入-技术方案》：`GET /ce/pm/v1/api/categories`、`GET /ce/pm/v1/api/event/list`。\n\nWiki: https://skyrocket.sg.larksuite.com/wiki/TEZgwnuyOiJ315kIRn1lypTZgce\n\n覆盖：正常路径、分页/状态/排序边界、多余 query、`categoryIds` 逗号写法（文档示例）、非法 `categoryId` 字符串等（不覆盖「GET 接口误用 POST」等非约定调用）。\n\n变量：`baseUrl`、`categoryId`。",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "baseUrl", "value": "https://api2-testnet.zoomex.com" },
    { "key": "categoryId", "value": "30101", "description": "测试用分类 id；可与 Wiki 示例 303/304/30501 等替换。" },
    { "key": "wikiDoc", "value": "https://skyrocket.sg.larksuite.com/wiki/TEZgwnuyOiJ315kIRn1lypTZgce", "description": "关联技术方案 Wiki 链接（只读说明）。" }
